  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription(sitePart==Wolfein_BattleSite_RebelSurround)->The colonists have intercepted an encrypted transmission from the Wolfein resistance. Although the message is heavily encrypted and fragmented, the few deciphered phrases suggest that they have successfully surrounded a small detachment of MegaCorp soldiers, and a firefight appears to be underway.\n\nWhether you intend to come to the aid of the MegaCorp troops, or simply wait for the resistance to prevail and then scavenge the remaining spoils, this is an opportunity that will not last long.</li>
    <li>questDescription(sitePart==Wolfein_BattleSite_Mechanoid)->The colonists have intercepted a plaintext transmission from the Wolfein resistance. The sender’s wording is hurried and disordered, making it clear that they are being ambushed by a large force of MegaCorp mechanoids. A call for aid has been broadcast to any nearby anti-MegaCorp forces, and the situation appears to be reaching a critical point.\n\nWhether you hold a grudge against this resistance group, or simply plan to arrive after the MegaCorp forces prevail to scavenge the remaining equipment and wreckage, this is an opportunity that will not last long.</li>
  -->
  <Wolfein_BattleSite.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription(sitePart==Wolfein_BattleSite_RebelSurround)->殖民者拦截到了一段来自沃芬族抵抗军的加密通信。尽管内容残缺且经过重度加密，但通过被破译出的零碎片段，你仍能勉强判断出：她们已成功包围了一小股军企士兵，战斗似乎正在进行中。\n\n无论你是打算出手援助这支军企小队，还是准备在抵抗军取得胜利后前往现场收集遗留的装备与战利品，这都是一个不会持续太久的机会。</li>
    <li>questDescription(sitePart==Wolfein_BattleSite_Mechanoid)->殖民者拦截到一条来自沃芬族抵抗军的明文通信。发信者的措辞急促而混乱，显然她们正遭到大批军企机械体的伏击，并正在向附近一切可能的反抗势力发出求援信号，战况已迫在眉睫。\n\n无论你与这支抵抗军是否结怨，还是仅仅打算在军企取得胜利后前往战场搜刮遗留的装备与残骸，这都是一个稍纵即逝的机会</li>
  </Wolfein_BattleSite.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
